## RLS AUDIT CHECKLIST

For each Supabase table, verify:

```markdown
### Table: [table_name]

- [ ] RLS enabled: `ALTER TABLE [table] ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;`
- [ ] SELECT policy: [policy name or MISSING]
- [ ] INSERT policy: [policy name or MISSING]  
- [ ] UPDATE policy: [policy name or MISSING]
- [ ] DELETE policy: [policy name or MISSING]
- [ ] Policies use auth.uid(): [Yes/No]
- [ ] Service role bypass documented: [Yes/No/N/A]
```

